# ovh_vrack_vps (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve information about a VPS attached to a vRack.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vrack_vps/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your vRack.
* `vps` - (Required) The service_name of the VPS.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vrack_vps.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the vRack VPS association.
* `service_name` - The service_name of the vRack.
* `vps` - The service_name of the VPS.
